{"tid":336154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡男深水埗街頭拳毆兩大叔兼扯頭髮 正義男挺身阻止","createTime":"2017-07-26T07:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T12:17:42.000Z","uid":82006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1ae493d653e11be1150bd54a7bc6053d204181","tid":336154,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:43:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170725&amp;guid=57001371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170725%26guid%3D57001371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=KpYxcfbBRDrKVsFuHxlYx%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5b422590\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170725%26guid%3D57001371%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=a493069b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170725&amp;guid=57001371&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，深水埗福華街161至165號外有人打架。讀者李小姐經過現場，目擊有人疑因搬貨阻塞問題起爭執，隨即發生打鬥，她於是拍下短片。片中所見，一名黑衫男子衝向路邊一輛七人車，揮拳毆向旁邊一名男子的臉部，對方即時被重拳擊中跌倒，其間一名女子上前制止亦被撞跌。<br />\n<br />\n黑衫男未肯罷休，再揮拳毆向客貨車上另一名男子，對方及時閃避，但黑衫男繼而扯着對方頭髮，把他拖倒在地上。此時附近一名穿紅色短褲的工人見狀，見義勇為立即跑至，把雙方分開，並喝止黑衣男：「阿叔嚟㗎，唔好X打啦！有咩事？女人你都打．．．冇嘢呀你？」、「有咩事呀你？打啲後生吖嘛．．．做嘢啫，唔使打人呀？」<br />\n<br />\n李小姐形容，事發前「雙方講唔夠兩句就打起上嚟」，涉事的黑衫男子「好暴躁，好似癲咗咁！」現場大批街坊圍觀，警方接報趕到調查，把受傷的一男一女送院治理，並拘捕一名男子。"},{"pid":"810dfa31fbf33bfb812522a1be89141ad79a14ea","tid":336154,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:43:48.000Z","msg":"有無人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f2ed6e7763d9650709cb86358dac7357853a6a","tid":336154,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f3158bc3b2645204ece186ad314eaa49df6a02de","tid":336154,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0